'''三氟化钯'''，又称'''氟化钯(II,IV)'''，是一种[[钯|钯]]和[[氟|氟]]形成的无机化合物。它的[[实验式|实验式]]是PdF<sub>3</sub>，但实际上它上一种[[混合价态化合物|混合价态化合物]]'''六氟合钯(IV)酸钯(II)'''（Pd<sup>II</sup>[Pd<sup>IV</sup>F<sub>6</sub>]），通常可以简写成Pd[PdF<sub>6</sub>]或Pd<sub>2</sub>F<sub>6</sub>。<ref name="G&E-1152-1153">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw2nd|pages=1152–1153}}</ref><ref name="Housecroft-788">{{Housecroft3rd|page=788}}</ref>

==制备==
Pd[PdF<sub>6</sub>]是氟气与金属钯反应最稳定的产物<ref name="G&E-1152-1153" />：

:<math>\rm \ 2Pd + 3F_2 \rightarrow Pd[PdF_6]</math>

也可用[[三氟化溴|三氟化溴]]与[[二氟化钯|二氟化钯]]反应，形成[[加合物|加合物]]Pd<sub>2</sub>F<sub>6</sub>·2BrF<sub>3</sub>，然后加热到180°C使该加合物分解得到三氟化钯：
:<math>\rm \ 2PdF_2 + 3BrF_3 \rightarrow Pd_2F_6</math>·<math>\rm \ 2BrF_3 + BrF</math>

==结构和性质==
Pd[PdF<sub>6</sub>]具有[[顺磁性|顺磁性]]，[[晶体结构|晶体]]中Pd(II)和Pd(IV)都采用八面体配位形式。<ref name="Housecroft-788" /><ref name="Jack">{{ cite journal | journal = [[Acta_Crystallographica|Acta Cryst.]] | year = 1957 | volume = 10 | pages = 63–69 | title = The crystal structures of the trifluorides of iron, cobalt, ruthenium, rhodium, palladium and iridium | first1 = M. A. | last1 = Hepworth | first2 = K. H. | last2 = Jack | first3 = R. D. | last3 = Peacock | first4 = G. J. | last4 = Westland | doi = 10.1107/S0365110X57000158 }}</ref>Pd<sup>II</sup>-F键的键长为2.17 Å，而Pd<sup>IV</sup>-F键的键长较短，是1.90 Å。<ref name="Tressaud">{{ cite journal | last1 = Tressaud | first1 = A. | last2 = Bartlett | first2 = N. | authorlink2 = Neil Bartlett (chemist) | year = 2001 | title = Preparation, Magnetic Properties, and Pressure-Induced Transitions of Some M<sup>II</sup>M<sup>IV</sup>F<sub>6</sub> (M<sup>II</sup>=Ni, Pd, Cu; M<sup>IV</sup>=Pd, Pt, Sn) Complex Fluorides | journal = [[Journal_of_Solid_State_Chemistry|J. Solid State Chem.]] | volume = 162 | pages = 333–340 | doi = 10.1006/jssc.2001.9331 }}</ref>

